---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base title="Cookies & Tracking" description="How Primo Guides uses cookies and tracking.">
  <div class="legal-wrap">
    <h1>Cookies &amp; Tracking</h1>
    <p class="updated">Last updated: June 2026</p>

    <p>We keep this minimal.</p>

    <h2>Essential</h2>
    <p>Only what's needed to serve the site. No tracking.</p>

    <h2>Analytics (no consent required)</h2>
    <p>We use Cloudflare Web Analytics — aggregate, non-identifying, used solely to improve the site, never for advertising, and never shared with third parties. This falls under the PECR "statistical purposes" exception (Data (Use and Access) Act 2025). You can opt out by using a browser content blocker.</p>

    <h2>Embedded YouTube video</h2>
    <p>Videos load only when you click play, at which point YouTube may set its own cookies. Don't want them? Don't press play — the written walkthrough needs no third-party cookies.</p>

    <h2>What we don't use</h2>
    <p>No advertising cookies, no profiling, no social media trackers. If that ever changes, we will ask for your consent first.</p>
  </div>
</Base>
